wiki.content: "ANTES QUE SE ACABE" is a song recorded by Purto rican artist Bad Bunny for his third solo album "EL ÚLTIMO TOUR DEL MUNDO", In "ANTES QUE SE ACABE", Bad Bunny makes an ode to life, happiness and joy. Beginning and ending with a sample that expresses good wishes, Benito seeks to take his listeners on a journey of joy, whose purpose is to value the present and promote messages of a positive nature, mentioning equality and looking for the positive side even on the most recent day. sad. This journey is made without losing its essence, since the beat is a kind of happy trap, which remains faithful to the rhythm and kicks of this genre, but adds elements of future bass, electronic music and a small nod to reggaeton. end of the second verse. All these elements together manage to form a kind of happy and hopeful trap, similar to what “Estamos Bien” was. Read more on Last.fm.
